data.description: Welcome to Monrovia,! Nestled in this Fabulous Frederick County Location, Close to All the Commuter Routes yet Tucked into a Private Forest of Trees this Rancher is Situated on Over 2 Acres of Land.  As You Enter this Charming Rancher the Large Living Room with a Cozy Wood Burning Fireplace and Hardwood Floors Wraps to the Fully Renovated Kitchen Complimented by  Butcher Block Counters and Stainless Appliances. This Open Floor Plan with Dining Area and Spacious Family Room Offers New Carpet and Light Fixtures and Views of Nature from Every Window!  Offering 3 Bedrooms and 2 Full Bathrooms on the Main Living Level. The Fully Finished  Lower Level Boast a Large Recreation Room with Wood Stove , Full Renovated Bathroom , Additional Space in Lower Level for Overflow Visitors or Office/Den/Workout Room, Laundry Room /Utility Room and Plenty of Storage! This Home Is Wired and Ready To Go For a Back Up Generator! Peace of Mind Knowing this Roof Over Your Head is Only 2 years Young!! Relax Outside on Your "Party Porch" a Covered Area Connecting Between the Home and the Huge Garage! Warm and Welcoming Entertain Under the Natural Pergola and Quaint Tiled Footing . Bring Your Love for the Outdoors! Need Lots of Space? We Got You Covered...  In This Huge  Detached Workshop with Electric, and Separate Shed. Plenty of Room for Parking ! Enjoy the Exciting Opportunities this Home Offers and  Flexibility of NO HOA or City Taxes!
